high_descs: Walk to the opposite side of the room then enter the bedroom and walk around the bed and in front of the dresser at the foot of the bed.
Pick up the onion on the dresser.
Walk back into the living room to the diningtable with the microwave on it.
Place the onion on the diningtable.
Return to the dresser in the bedroom and locate the same dresser.
Pick up the other onion on the dresser.
Take this onion to the diningtable in the living room with the microwave.
Place this onion next to the first onion on the diningtable to the right of the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Collect all the onions in the bedroom and take to the dining table in living room.

high_descs: Turn right to see a sofa in front, leave the room through an exit in the upper right side of the room, notice a box of drawers next to a nightstand upfront, and go in front of the dresser's shorter left side.
Pick up the onion from the box of drawers.
Head back to the room you came from, and turn to the diningtable on your left.
Place the onion on the diningtable.
Go back to the same place at the dresser you went to last time.
Pick up the onion from the box of drawers.
Move back to the diningtable.
Place the onion on the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Put two pieces of onion on the diningtable

high_descs: Turn right and head straight, turn right and head straight and then hang left towards the room corner, then turn right on the dresser.
Pick up the onion from the table.
Turn right and head straight, turn right and head straight and then hang left on the diningtable.
Place the onion on the diningtable.
Turn left and head straight, turn right and head straight to the dresser and then hang left, then turn right on the dresser.
Pick up the onion from the table.
Turn right and head straight, turn right and head straight and then hang left on the diningtable.
Place the onion on the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Collecting onion from different parts of the house and arranging them on the DiningTable.
